reviewText:
This is a compact and portable power bank. Now all of my phones/ipad will be fast charged and do not have to wait longer to be back up. The power bank has a rounded design and a rubber coating finish, making it stain resistant and providing good grip while holding the device.
The small LED flashlight is very useful.  The carrying pouch is really a nice add-on;
The power bank comes with 4 LED indicators showing the power banks battery life.

In general I like it.
Pros:
* easy to set up.
* many mounting options;
* good angles;
* does not fall off/detach;
* acceptable phone holding capability.

Cons:
* a bit noisy on the bumpy road;
* would press your side buttons when putting the phone in(differs from phone model to phone model);
* since the buttons are covered - you cannot press them :)(differs from phone model to phone model);

